## Escorts Overview Page

### URL
- `/alle-escorts/` (NL) / `/en/escorts/` (EN)

### Target Metrics
- **Word count**: 300-500 words
- **Read time**: <2 minutes
- **Primary function**: Navigation hub to all escort profiles

### Required Sections (In Order)

#### 1. Hero Section
- **H1**: "Onze Escorts" or "Alle Beschikbare Escorts"
- **Intro**: 2 sentences describing the selection and quality standards
- **Primary CTA**: Integrated into filter bar

#### 2. Filter Bar
- **Required filters**: City, Type/Attribute, Availability (Now/Today/This Week)
- **Optional filters**: Price range, Services offered
- **Behavior**: URL-based filtering for SEO (e.g., `/alle-escorts/?city=amsterdam`)

#### 3. Escort Grid
- **Default sort**: Availability, then featured status
- **Card content**: Photo, name, tagline, key stats, availability indicator
- **Pagination**: 12-16 profiles per page, numbered pagination (not infinite scroll)

#### 4. Value Proposition Strip
- **Format**: Compact USP bar below grid
- **Content**: 3 trust signals (selection process, discretion, availability)

#### 5. CTA Section
- **Format**: Simple banner
- **Content**: "Niet gevonden wat je zoekt? Neem contact op" with contact link

### SEO Requirements
- **Schema**: ItemList with escort profiles
- **Pagination**: rel="next"/rel="prev" for paginated results
- **Canonical**: Self-referencing, filtered views use canonical to base URL

### Content to Avoid
- Long introductory essays
- Repeated service descriptions
- Duplicate content from homepage

